gy scales, and will aid the push toward the\nobservational regime of nanoflares, which are a possible source of significant\ncoronal heating.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 28 Mar 2020 18:44:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-31"}
