opose a suboptimal algorithm to tackle\nthe GEE maximization problem with guaranteed convergence, capitalizing on the\napproaches of alternating optimization, fractional programming, and sequential\noptimization. Numerical results substantiate the effectiveness of the proposed\napproach as well as the considerable GEE gains provided by the RIS-assisted\ntransmission scheme over the traditional baselines.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 29 Mar 2020 12:47:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-14"}
